ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectOrder Approving the Boundary Change of The Napanee and District Chamber of Commerce
PrecisOrder approving the application by THE NAPANEE AND DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Ontario, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from Napanee Richmond township, North and South Fredricksburgh townships and Camden East township, Adolphustown township and Sheffield township to the County of Lennox and Addington, that includes the Town of Greater Napanee, the Township of Addington Highlands, Loyalist Township and the Township of Stone Mills
